#freemovies #moviesondemand #fullmovie

metadata.Plot: After her only friend is expelled from their private school in the Upper East Side of Manhattan, Cat Storm wants to get close to a boy she is attracted to and recreate herself with new friends. But her new friends are unreliable, her boyfriend is troubled, her parents are cold and indifferent, and she increasingly finds herself unloved.
metadata.Actors: Dominique Swain, Brad Renfro, Bijou Phillips
